Attempted to import the "Labmatrix Core" space with the "LABMATRIX" key from internally hosted Confluence 4.1 XML export twice and received the following error reading:

Import failed. Check your server logs for more information. com.atlassian.confluence.importexport.ImportExportException: Unable to complete import because the data does not match the constraints in the Confluence schema. Cause: PSQLException: ERROR: duplicate key value violates unique constraint "os_propertyentry_pkey"

I also received a message that directed me to this page to report this bug. I attached a screenshot of the error screen.

